  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Age ≥ 18 years

          -  Onset of stroke less than 14 days

          -  First ischemic stroke causing lower limb weakness (MRC score ≤4 in knee extensors) and
             gait impairment

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Contraindications to MRI or TMS

          -  Other neurological disorders

          -  Significant somatic or psychiatric disorders

          -  History of seizures

          -  Language or cognitive disorders prohibiting participation
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
